{"tid":2083890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"71維園見","createTime":"2020-06-29T04:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T07:49:33.000Z","uid":121173,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d73632caddefac1f1fd29cf7244c0a9cad4eb20f","tid":2083890,"uid":121173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"多你一個好多<br />\n手足71維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2054dba52b47ba28bc302d354e73d0750bf0663b","tid":2083890,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:59:14.000Z","msg":"71 71 71 71 71 71 71 71 71 71"},{"pid":"733f3cb90df8035caf11a871ab73d90723f2b920","tid":2083890,"uid":121173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:33:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8197cc8e5b791fc8aca96878fa6db507ec349cbb","tid":2083890,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0824a8c32792d04d407cb4251b65cea675df6868","tid":2083890,"uid":23629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:44:11.000Z","msg":"71"},{"pid":"cf7e84a04aad29580d15b945bb1c913e995f57be","tid":2083890,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:44:14.000Z","msg":"71見<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8VgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=eb366605\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4fcc3b8f303b7664c55c6c326e70ef395f468f97","tid":2083890,"uid":250036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"71見"},{"pid":"91b6e28a9cd42fe88d82da2f82b0fef42d33bec2","tid":2083890,"uid":258055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbf83cdeb062c6d174693528e8cca989bda108d9","tid":2083890,"uid":154490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:51:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cac2ff730b5b925fdba6c709854d173324137572","tid":2083890,"uid":226515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ad2b3998ae7530f568c88cd2cb67c2ef1f969b","tid":2083890,"uid":80478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72a6aa85b8f00dcbc307250b6ba02e3aa64329f3","tid":2083890,"uid":78194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ffa4156847c5e98b5314cdc4da7f749e8bdb33","tid":2083890,"uid":48061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"7.1維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fed310a6f8ba8474fbc2e0e79dfef2e0bfb73e","tid":2083890,"uid":199718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306b6db9225622b034749fe805777b5cc71bf8cf","tid":2083890,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"372bfb896a3850d9b0c55321b8c45da41fc0bfc9","tid":2083890,"uid":198684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bca4a75750d324d36e94ae51cf2225216a4d7b55","tid":2083890,"uid":13853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30491bb910752d9e2b3653f1d41846349097bf86","tid":2083890,"uid":188035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d73632caddefac1f1fd29cf7244c0a9cad4eb20f","tid":2083890,"uid":121173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"